{
  "video_id": "nO69Njad-ec",
  "title": "A simple new blood test that can catch cancer early | Jimmy Lin",
  "es": 0,
  "json": [
    {
      "index": 1,
      "start_time": 13573.0,
      "end_time": 14740.0,
      "text": "Cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 2,
      "start_time": 15121.0,
      "end_time": 18186.0,
      "text": "Many of us have lost family, friends or loved ones"
    },
    {
      "index": 3,
      "start_time": 18210.0,
      "end_time": 19890.0,
      "text": "to this horrible disease."
    },
    {
      "index": 4,
      "start_time": 19914.0,
      "end_time": 22100.0,
      "text": "I know there are some of you in the audience"
    },
    {
      "index": 5,
      "start_time": 22340.0,
      "end_time": 23275.0,
      "text": "who are cancer survivors,"
    },
    {
      "index": 6,
      "start_time": 23299.0,
      "end_time": 25454.0,
      "text": "or who are fighting cancer at this moment."
    },
    {
      "index": 7,
      "start_time": 25478.0,
      "end_time": 27469.0,
      "text": "My heart goes out to you."
    },
    {
      "index": 8,
      "start_time": 27493.0,
      "end_time": 32766.0,
      "text": "While this word often conjures up emotions of sadness and anger and fear,"
    },
    {
      "index": 9,
      "start_time": 32791.0,
      "end_time": 36305.0,
      "text": "I bring you good news from the front lines of cancer research."
    },
    {
      "index": 10,
      "start_time": 36329.0,
      "end_time": 40189.0,
      "text": "The fact is, we are starting to win the war on cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 11,
      "start_time": 41138.0,
      "end_time": 42841.0,
      "text": "In fact, we lie at the intersection"
    },
    {
      "index": 12,
      "start_time": 42865.0,
      "end_time": 47540.0,
      "text": "of the three of the most exciting developments within cancer research."
    },
    {
      "index": 13,
      "start_time": 47780.0,
      "end_time": 49363.0,
      "text": "The first is cancer genomics."
    },
    {
      "index": 14,
      "start_time": 49387.0,
      "end_time": 51412.0,
      "text": "The genome is a composition"
    },
    {
      "index": 15,
      "start_time": 51436.0,
      "end_time": 54372.0,
      "text": "of all the genetic information encoded by DNA"
    },
    {
      "index": 16,
      "start_time": 54396.0,
      "end_time": 55763.0,
      "text": "in an organism."
    },
    {
      "index": 17,
      "start_time": 55787.0,
      "end_time": 58628.0,
      "text": "In cancers, changes in the DNA called mutations"
    },
    {
      "index": 18,
      "start_time": 58652.0,
      "end_time": 61454.0,
      "text": "are what drive these cancers to go out of control."
    },
    {
      "index": 19,
      "start_time": 61890.0,
      "end_time": 65182.0,
      "text": "Around 10 years ago, I was part of the team at Johns Hopkins"
    },
    {
      "index": 20,
      "start_time": 65206.0,
      "end_time": 67804.0,
      "text": "that first mapped the mutations of cancers."
    },
    {
      "index": 21,
      "start_time": 67828.0,
      "end_time": 70140.0,
      "text": "We did this first for colorectal,"
    },
    {
      "index": 22,
      "start_time": 70380.0,
      "end_time": 72564.0,
      "text": "breast, pancreatic and brain cancers."
    },
    {
      "index": 23,
      "start_time": 72984.0,
      "end_time": 76496.0,
      "text": "And since then, there have been over 90 projects in 70 countries"
    },
    {
      "index": 24,
      "start_time": 76520.0,
      "end_time": 78110.0,
      "text": "all over the world,"
    },
    {
      "index": 25,
      "start_time": 78134.0,
      "end_time": 81509.0,
      "text": "working to understand the genetic basis of these diseases."
    },
    {
      "index": 26,
      "start_time": 81533.0,
      "end_time": 84587.0,
      "text": "Today, tens of thousands of cancers are understood"
    },
    {
      "index": 27,
      "start_time": 84611.0,
      "end_time": 86906.0,
      "text": "down to exquisite molecular detail."
    },
    {
      "index": 28,
      "start_time": 88200.0,
      "end_time": 90322.0,
      "text": "The second revolution is precision medicine,"
    },
    {
      "index": 29,
      "start_time": 90346.0,
      "end_time": 92750.0,
      "text": "also known as \"personalized medicine.\""
    },
    {
      "index": 30,
      "start_time": 92774.0,
      "end_time": 96351.0,
      "text": "Instead of one-size-fits-all methods to be able to treat cancers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 31,
      "start_time": 96375.0,
      "end_time": 100300.0,
      "text": "there is a whole new class of drugs that are able to target cancers"
    },
    {
      "index": 32,
      "start_time": 100540.0,
      "end_time": 102261.0,
      "text": "based on their unique genetic profile."
    },
    {
      "index": 33,
      "start_time": 102737.0,
      "end_time": 105667.0,
      "text": "Today, there are a host of these tailor-made drugs,"
    },
    {
      "index": 34,
      "start_time": 105691.0,
      "end_time": 107210.0,
      "text": "called targeted therapies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 35,
      "start_time": 107450.0,
      "end_time": 109228.0,
      "text": "available to physicians even today"
    },
    {
      "index": 36,
      "start_time": 109252.0,
      "end_time": 112515.0,
      "text": "to be able to personalize their therapy for their patients,"
    },
    {
      "index": 37,
      "start_time": 112539.0,
      "end_time": 114465.0,
      "text": "and many others are in development."
    },
    {
      "index": 38,
      "start_time": 115116.0,
      "end_time": 118414.0,
      "text": "The third exciting revolution is immunotherapy,"
    },
    {
      "index": 39,
      "start_time": 118438.0,
      "end_time": 120214.0,
      "text": "and this is really exciting."
    },
    {
      "index": 40,
      "start_time": 120865.0,
      "end_time": 123574.0,
      "text": "Scientists have been able to leverage the immune system"
    },
    {
      "index": 41,
      "start_time": 123599.0,
      "end_time": 125940.0,
      "text": "in the fight against cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 42,
      "start_time": 125652.0,
      "end_time": 129848.0,
      "text": "For example, there have been ways where we find the off switches of cancer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 43,
      "start_time": 129872.00000000001,
      "end_time": 133316.0,
      "text": "and new drugs have been able to turn the immune system back on,"
    },
    {
      "index": 44,
      "start_time": 133340.0,
      "end_time": 134928.0,
      "text": "to be able to fight cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 45,
      "start_time": 134952.0,
      "end_time": 139430.0,
      "text": "In addition, there are ways where you can take away immune cells"
    },
    {
      "index": 46,
      "start_time": 139670.0,
      "end_time": 140227.0,
      "text": "from the body,"
    },
    {
      "index": 47,
      "start_time": 140251.0,
      "end_time": 143338.0,
      "text": "train them, engineer them and put them back into the body"
    },
    {
      "index": 48,
      "start_time": 143362.0,
      "end_time": 144739.0,
      "text": "to fight cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 49,
      "start_time": 144763.0,
      "end_time": 147441.0,
      "text": "Almost sounds like science fiction, doesn&#39;t it?"
    },
    {
      "index": 50,
      "start_time": 147910.0,
      "end_time": 150926.0,
      "text": "While I was a researcher at the National Cancer Institute,"
    },
    {
      "index": 51,
      "start_time": 150950.0,
      "end_time": 154405.0,
      "text": "I had the privilege of working with some of the pioneers of this field"
    },
    {
      "index": 52,
      "start_time": 154429.0,
      "end_time": 156675.0,
      "text": "and watched the development firsthand."
    },
    {
      "index": 53,
      "start_time": 156699.0,
      "end_time": 158142.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s been pretty amazing."
    },
    {
      "index": 54,
      "start_time": 158166.0,
      "end_time": 161171.0,
      "text": "Today, over 600 clinical trials are open,"
    },
    {
      "index": 55,
      "start_time": 161195.0,
      "end_time": 165380.0,
      "text": "actively recruiting patients to explore all aspects in immunotherapy."
    },
    {
      "index": 56,
      "start_time": 166484.0,
      "end_time": 169545.0,
      "text": "While these three exciting revolutions are ongoing,"
    },
    {
      "index": 57,
      "start_time": 169569.0,
      "end_time": 171593.0,
      "text": "unfortunately, this is only the beginning,"
    },
    {
      "index": 58,
      "start_time": 171617.0,
      "end_time": 174828.0,
      "text": "and there are still many, many challenges."
    },
    {
      "index": 59,
      "start_time": 174852.0,
      "end_time": 176601.0,
      "text": "Let me illustrate with a patient."
    },
    {
      "index": 60,
      "start_time": 178210.0,
      "end_time": 180932.0,
      "text": "Here is a patient with a skin cancer called melanoma."
    },
    {
      "index": 61,
      "start_time": 180956.0,
      "end_time": 184300.0,
      "text": "It&#39;s horrible; the cancer has gone everywhere."
    },
    {
      "index": 62,
      "start_time": 185260.0,
      "end_time": 188746.0,
      "text": "However, scientists were able to map the mutations of this cancer"
    },
    {
      "index": 63,
      "start_time": 188770.0,
      "end_time": 192826.0,
      "text": "and give a specific treatment that targets one of the mutations."
    },
    {
      "index": 64,
      "start_time": 193770.0,
      "end_time": 196223.0,
      "text": "And the result is almost miraculous."
    },
    {
      "index": 65,
      "start_time": 196247.0,
      "end_time": 198693.0,
      "text": "Tumors almost seem to melt away."
    },
    {
      "index": 66,
      "start_time": 199730.0,
      "end_time": 202242.0,
      "text": "Unfortunately, this is not the end of the story."
    },
    {
      "index": 67,
      "start_time": 202897.0,
      "end_time": 205376.0,
      "text": "A few months later, this picture is taken."
    },
    {
      "index": 68,
      "start_time": 205977.0,
      "end_time": 207464.0,
      "text": "The tumor has come back."
    },
    {
      "index": 69,
      "start_time": 208447.0,
      "end_time": 210270.0,
      "text": "The question is: Why?"
    },
    {
      "index": 70,
      "start_time": 210712.0,
      "end_time": 213143.0,
      "text": "The answer is tumor heterogeneity."
    },
    {
      "index": 71,
      "start_time": 213927.0,
      "end_time": 215176.0,
      "text": "Let me explain."
    },
    {
      "index": 72,
      "start_time": 216944.0,
      "end_time": 220432.0,
      "text": "Even a cancer as small as one centimeter in diameter"
    },
    {
      "index": 73,
      "start_time": 220456.0,
      "end_time": 223149.0,
      "text": "harbors over a hundred million different cells."
    },
    {
      "index": 74,
      "start_time": 223668.0,
      "end_time": 225549.0,
      "text": "While genetically similar,"
    },
    {
      "index": 75,
      "start_time": 225573.0,
      "end_time": 228282.0,
      "text": "there are small differences in these different cancers"
    },
    {
      "index": 76,
      "start_time": 228306.0,
      "end_time": 231163.0,
      "text": "that make them differently prone to different drugs."
    },
    {
      "index": 77,
      "start_time": 231187.0,
      "end_time": 233615.0,
      "text": "So even if you have a drug that&#39;s highly effective,"
    },
    {
      "index": 78,
      "start_time": 233639.0,
      "end_time": 235374.0,
      "text": "that kills almost all the cells,"
    },
    {
      "index": 79,
      "start_time": 235398.0,
      "end_time": 238588.0,
      "text": "there is a chance that there&#39;s a small population"
    },
    {
      "index": 80,
      "start_time": 238612.0,
      "end_time": 240386.0,
      "text": "that&#39;s resistant to the drug."
    },
    {
      "index": 81,
      "start_time": 240410.0,
      "end_time": 242432.0,
      "text": "This ultimately is the population"
    },
    {
      "index": 82,
      "start_time": 242456.0,
      "end_time": 243619.0,
      "text": "that comes back,"
    },
    {
      "index": 83,
      "start_time": 243644.0,
      "end_time": 244962.0,
      "text": "and takes over the patient."
    },
    {
      "index": 84,
      "start_time": 245707.0,
      "end_time": 248566.0,
      "text": "So then the question is: What do we do with this information?"
    },
    {
      "index": 85,
      "start_time": 248590.0,
      "end_time": 249852.0,
      "text": "Well, the key, then,"
    },
    {
      "index": 86,
      "start_time": 249876.0,
      "end_time": 254746.0,
      "text": "is to apply all these exciting advancements in cancer therapy earlier,"
    },
    {
      "index": 87,
      "start_time": 254770.0,
      "end_time": 255992.0,
      "text": "as soon as we can,"
    },
    {
      "index": 88,
      "start_time": 256160.00000000003,
      "end_time": 258355.00000000003,
      "text": "before these resistance clones emerge."
    },
    {
      "index": 89,
      "start_time": 259500.0,
      "end_time": 263409.0,
      "text": "The key to cancer and curing cancer is early detection."
    },
    {
      "index": 90,
      "start_time": 264259.0,
      "end_time": 265928.0,
      "text": "And we intuitively know this."
    },
    {
      "index": 91,
      "start_time": 265952.0,
      "end_time": 269380.0,
      "text": "Finding cancer early results in better outcomes,"
    },
    {
      "index": 92,
      "start_time": 269620.0,
      "end_time": 271108.0,
      "text": "and the numbers show this as well."
    },
    {
      "index": 93,
      "start_time": 271132.0,
      "end_time": 275375.0,
      "text": "For example, in ovarian cancer, if you detect cancer in stage four,"
    },
    {
      "index": 94,
      "start_time": 275399.0,
      "end_time": 278528.0,
      "text": "only 17 percent of the women survive at five years."
    },
    {
      "index": 95,
      "start_time": 279880.0,
      "end_time": 283516.0,
      "text": "However, if you are able to detect this cancer as early as stage one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 96,
      "start_time": 283540.0,
      "end_time": 286232.0,
      "text": "over 92 percent of women will survive."
    },
    {
      "index": 97,
      "start_time": 286745.0,
      "end_time": 291548.0,
      "text": "But the sad fact is, only 15 percent of women are detected at stage one,"
    },
    {
      "index": 98,
      "start_time": 291572.0,
      "end_time": 297144.0,
      "text": "whereas the vast majority, 70 percent, are detected in stages three and four."
    },
    {
      "index": 99,
      "start_time": 297168.0,
      "end_time": 301349.0,
      "text": "We desperately need better detection mechanisms for cancers."
    },
    {
      "index": 100,
      "start_time": 301873.0,
      "end_time": 306151.0,
      "text": "The current best ways to screen cancer fall into one of three categories."
    },
    {
      "index": 101,
      "start_time": 306175.0,
      "end_time": 308350.0,
      "text": "First is medical procedures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 102,
      "start_time": 308374.0,
      "end_time": 311282.0,
      "text": "which is like colonoscopy for colon cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 103,
      "start_time": 311306.0,
      "end_time": 315921.0,
      "text": "Second is protein biomarkers, like PSA for prostate cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 104,
      "start_time": 315946.0,
      "end_time": 318858.0,
      "text": "Or third, imaging techniques,"
    },
    {
      "index": 105,
      "start_time": 318882.0,
      "end_time": 321245.0,
      "text": "such as mammography for breast cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 106,
      "start_time": 322239.0,
      "end_time": 324664.0,
      "text": "Medical procedures are the gold standard;"
    },
    {
      "index": 107,
      "start_time": 324689.0,
      "end_time": 326785.0,
      "text": "however, they are highly invasive"
    },
    {
      "index": 108,
      "start_time": 326809.0,
      "end_time": 329614.0,
      "text": "and require a large infrastructure to implement."
    },
    {
      "index": 109,
      "start_time": 330502.0,
      "end_time": 333706.0,
      "text": "Protein markers, while effective in some populations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 110,
      "start_time": 333730.0,
      "end_time": 336219.0,
      "text": "are not very specific in some circumstances,"
    },
    {
      "index": 111,
      "start_time": 336243.0,
      "end_time": 338826.0,
      "text": "resulting in high numbers of false positives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 112,
      "start_time": 338850.0,
      "end_time": 344550.0,
      "text": "which then results in unnecessary work-ups and unnecessary procedures."
    },
    {
      "index": 113,
      "start_time": 345142.0,
      "end_time": 348106.0,
      "text": "Imaging methods, while useful in some populations,"
    },
    {
      "index": 114,
      "start_time": 348781.0,
      "end_time": 351678.0,
      "text": "expose patients to harmful radiation."
    },
    {
      "index": 115,
      "start_time": 351702.0,
      "end_time": 354316.0,
      "text": "In addition, it is not applicable to all patients."
    },
    {
      "index": 116,
      "start_time": 354340.0,
      "end_time": 358383.0,
      "text": "For example, mammography has problems in women with dense breasts."
    },
    {
      "index": 117,
      "start_time": 358856.0,
      "end_time": 362250.0,
      "text": "So what we need is a method that is noninvasive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 118,
      "start_time": 362274.0,
      "end_time": 364410.0,
      "text": "that is light in infrastructure,"
    },
    {
      "index": 119,
      "start_time": 364650.0,
      "end_time": 365328.0,
      "text": "that is highly specific,"
    },
    {
      "index": 120,
      "start_time": 365968.0,
      "end_time": 369189.0,
      "text": "that also does not have false positives,"
    },
    {
      "index": 121,
      "start_time": 369213.0,
      "end_time": 371179.0,
      "text": "does not use any radiation"
    },
    {
      "index": 122,
      "start_time": 371203.0,
      "end_time": 374133.0,
      "text": "and is applicable to large populations."
    },
    {
      "index": 123,
      "start_time": 374158.0,
      "end_time": 375332.0,
      "text": "Even more importantly,"
    },
    {
      "index": 124,
      "start_time": 375356.0,
      "end_time": 377552.0,
      "text": "we need a method to be able to detect cancers"
    },
    {
      "index": 125,
      "start_time": 377576.0,
      "end_time": 380268.0,
      "text": "before they&#39;re 100 million cells in size."
    },
    {
      "index": 126,
      "start_time": 380880.0,
      "end_time": 382445.0,
      "text": "Does such a technology exist?"
    },
    {
      "index": 127,
      "start_time": 382828.0,
      "end_time": 385748.0,
      "text": "Well, I wouldn&#39;t be up here giving a talk if it didn&#39;t."
    },
    {
      "index": 128,
      "start_time": 386722.0,
      "end_time": 390193.0,
      "text": "I&#39;m excited to tell you about this latest technology we&#39;ve developed."
    },
    {
      "index": 129,
      "start_time": 391350.0,
      "end_time": 393737.0,
      "text": "Central to our technology is a simple blood test."
    },
    {
      "index": 130,
      "start_time": 394202.0,
      "end_time": 397932.0,
      "text": "The blood circulatory system, while seemingly mundane,"
    },
    {
      "index": 131,
      "start_time": 397956.0,
      "end_time": 400286.0,
      "text": "is essential for you to survive,"
    },
    {
      "index": 132,
      "start_time": 400310.0,
      "end_time": 402815.0,
      "text": "providing oxygen and nutrients to your cells,"
    },
    {
      "index": 133,
      "start_time": 402839.0,
      "end_time": 405444.0,
      "text": "and removing waste and carbon dioxide."
    },
    {
      "index": 134,
      "start_time": 405468.0,
      "end_time": 407321.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s a key biological insight:"
    },
    {
      "index": 135,
      "start_time": 408240.0,
      "end_time": 411323.0,
      "text": "Cancer cells grow and die faster than normal cells,"
    },
    {
      "index": 136,
      "start_time": 411347.0,
      "end_time": 412543.0,
      "text": "and when they die,"
    },
    {
      "index": 137,
      "start_time": 412567.0,
      "end_time": 415288.0,
      "text": "DNA is shed into the blood system."
    },
    {
      "index": 138,
      "start_time": 415312.0,
      "end_time": 418820.0,
      "text": "Since we know the signatures of these cancer cells"
    },
    {
      "index": 139,
      "start_time": 418106.0,
      "end_time": 420810.0,
      "text": "from all the different cancer genome sequencing projects,"
    },
    {
      "index": 140,
      "start_time": 420834.0,
      "end_time": 422875.0,
      "text": "we can look for those signals in the blood"
    },
    {
      "index": 141,
      "start_time": 422899.0,
      "end_time": 425710.0,
      "text": "to be able to detect these cancers early."
    },
    {
      "index": 142,
      "start_time": 426229.0,
      "end_time": 430270.0,
      "text": "So instead of waiting for cancers to be large enough to cause symptoms,"
    },
    {
      "index": 143,
      "start_time": 430520.0,
      "end_time": 432951.0,
      "text": "or for them to be dense enough to show up on imaging,"
    },
    {
      "index": 144,
      "start_time": 432975.0,
      "end_time": 435417.0,
      "text": "or for them to be prominent enough"
    },
    {
      "index": 145,
      "start_time": 435441.0,
      "end_time": 438681.0,
      "text": "for you to be able to visualize on medical procedures,"
    },
    {
      "index": 146,
      "start_time": 438705.0,
      "end_time": 442697.0,
      "text": "we can start looking for cancers while they are relatively pretty small,"
    },
    {
      "index": 147,
      "start_time": 442721.0,
      "end_time": 446325.0,
      "text": "by looking for these small amounts of DNA in the blood."
    },
    {
      "index": 148,
      "start_time": 447635.0,
      "end_time": 449310.0,
      "text": "So let me tell you how we do this."
    },
    {
      "index": 149,
      "start_time": 449334.0,
      "end_time": 452198.0,
      "text": "First, like I said, we start off with a simple blood test --"
    },
    {
      "index": 150,
      "start_time": 452222.0,
      "end_time": 454796.0,
      "text": "no radiation, no complicated equipment --"
    },
    {
      "index": 151,
      "start_time": 454821.0,
      "end_time": 456287.0,
      "text": "a simple blood test."
    },
    {
      "index": 152,
      "start_time": 456311.0,
      "end_time": 457847.0,
      "text": "Then the blood is shipped to us,"
    },
    {
      "index": 153,
      "start_time": 457871.0,
      "end_time": 460260.0,
      "text": "and what we do is extract the DNA out of it."
    },
    {
      "index": 154,
      "start_time": 460930.0,
      "end_time": 463326.0,
      "text": "While your body is mostly healthy cells,"
    },
    {
      "index": 155,
      "start_time": 463350.0,
      "end_time": 466996.0,
      "text": "most of the DNA that&#39;s detected will be from healthy cells."
    },
    {
      "index": 156,
      "start_time": 467654.0,
      "end_time": 470721.0,
      "text": "However, there will be a small amount, less than one percent,"
    },
    {
      "index": 157,
      "start_time": 470745.0,
      "end_time": 472477.0,
      "text": "that comes from the cancer cells."
    },
    {
      "index": 158,
      "start_time": 473365.0,
      "end_time": 477571.0,
      "text": "Then we use molecular biology methods to be able to enrich this DNA"
    },
    {
      "index": 159,
      "start_time": 477595.0,
      "end_time": 482700.0,
      "text": "for areas of the genome which are known to be associated with cancer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 160,
      "start_time": 482310.0,
      "end_time": 484984.0,
      "text": "based on the information from the cancer genomics projects."
    },
    {
      "index": 161,
      "start_time": 485484.0,
      "end_time": 489361.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re able to then put this DNA into DNA-sequencing machines"
    },
    {
      "index": 162,
      "start_time": 489385.0,
      "end_time": 494750.0,
      "text": "and are able to digitize the DNA into A&#39;s, C&#39;s, T&#39;s and G&#39;s"
    },
    {
      "index": 163,
      "start_time": 494990.0,
      "end_time": 495697.0,
      "text": "and have this final readout."
    },
    {
      "index": 164,
      "start_time": 496271.0,
      "end_time": 502261.0,
      "text": "Ultimately, we have information of billions of letters"
    },
    {
      "index": 165,
      "start_time": 502285.0,
      "end_time": 505295.0,
      "text": "that output from this run."
    },
    {
      "index": 166,
      "start_time": 506455.0,
      "end_time": 509675.0,
      "text": "We then apply statistical and computational methods"
    },
    {
      "index": 167,
      "start_time": 509699.0,
      "end_time": 512371.0,
      "text": "to be able to find the small signal that&#39;s present,"
    },
    {
      "index": 168,
      "start_time": 512395.0,
      "end_time": 516500.0,
      "text": "indicative of the small amount of cancer DNA in the blood."
    },
    {
      "index": 169,
      "start_time": 517970.0,
      "end_time": 519522.0,
      "text": "So does this actually work in patients?"
    },
    {
      "index": 170,
      "start_time": 519547.0,
      "end_time": 523370.0,
      "text": "Well, because there&#39;s no way of really predicting right now"
    },
    {
      "index": 171,
      "start_time": 523610.0,
      "end_time": 524569.0,
      "text": "which patients will get cancer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 172,
      "start_time": 524593.0,
      "end_time": 526650.0,
      "text": "we use the next best population:"
    },
    {
      "index": 173,
      "start_time": 527261.0,
      "end_time": 528695.0,
      "text": "cancers in remission;"
    },
    {
      "index": 174,
      "start_time": 529372.0,
      "end_time": 531794.0,
      "text": "specifically, lung cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 175,
      "start_time": 532225.0,
      "end_time": 535534.0,
      "text": "The sad fact is, even with the best drugs that we have today,"
    },
    {
      "index": 176,
      "start_time": 535558.0,
      "end_time": 537770.0,
      "text": "most lung cancers come back."
    },
    {
      "index": 177,
      "start_time": 537794.0,
      "end_time": 539930.0,
      "text": "The key, then, is to see"
    },
    {
      "index": 178,
      "start_time": 539118.0,
      "end_time": 542769.0,
      "text": "whether we&#39;re able to detect these recurrences of cancers"
    },
    {
      "index": 179,
      "start_time": 542793.0,
      "end_time": 544660.0,
      "text": "earlier than with standard methods."
    },
    {
      "index": 180,
      "start_time": 545159.0,
      "end_time": 547536.0,
      "text": "We just finished a major trial"
    },
    {
      "index": 181,
      "start_time": 547560.0,
      "end_time": 551306.0,
      "text": "with Professor Charles Swanton at University College London,"
    },
    {
      "index": 182,
      "start_time": 551331.0,
      "end_time": 552497.0,
      "text": "examining this."
    },
    {
      "index": 183,
      "start_time": 552521.0,
      "end_time": 555390.0,
      "text": "Let me walk you through an example of one patient."
    },
    {
      "index": 184,
      "start_time": 556586.0,
      "end_time": 559413.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s an example of one patient who undergoes surgery"
    },
    {
      "index": 185,
      "start_time": 559437.0,
      "end_time": 560605.0,
      "text": "at time point zero,"
    },
    {
      "index": 186,
      "start_time": 560629.0,
      "end_time": 563111.0,
      "text": "and then undergoes chemotherapy."
    },
    {
      "index": 187,
      "start_time": 563529.0,
      "end_time": 566140.0,
      "text": "Then the patient is under remission."
    },
    {
      "index": 188,
      "start_time": 566380.0,
      "end_time": 570647.0,
      "text": "He is monitored using clinical exams and imaging methods."
    },
    {
      "index": 189,
      "start_time": 570969.0,
      "end_time": 575872.0,
      "text": "Around day 450, unfortunately, the cancer comes back."
    },
    {
      "index": 190,
      "start_time": 577860.0,
      "end_time": 579571.0,
      "text": "The question is: Are we able to catch this earlier?"
    },
    {
      "index": 191,
      "start_time": 579595.0,
      "end_time": 583340.0,
      "text": "During this whole time, we&#39;ve been collecting blood serially"
    },
    {
      "index": 192,
      "start_time": 583364.0,
      "end_time": 586642.0,
      "text": "to be able to measure the amount of ctDNA in the blood."
    },
    {
      "index": 193,
      "start_time": 587380.0,
      "end_time": 590677.0,
      "text": "So at the initial time point, as expected,"
    },
    {
      "index": 194,
      "start_time": 590701.0,
      "end_time": 594399.0,
      "text": "there&#39;s a high level of cancer DNA in the blood."
    },
    {
      "index": 195,
      "start_time": 594423.0,
      "end_time": 598900.0,
      "text": "However, this goes away to zero in subsequent time points"
    },
    {
      "index": 196,
      "start_time": 598114.0,
      "end_time": 601571.0,
      "text": "and remains negligible after subsequent points."
    },
    {
      "index": 197,
      "start_time": 602813.0,
      "end_time": 608860.0,
      "text": "However, around day 340, we see the rise of cancer DNA in the blood,"
    },
    {
      "index": 198,
      "start_time": 608110.0,
      "end_time": 612675.0,
      "text": "and eventually, it goes up higher for days 400 and 450."
    },
    {
      "index": 199,
      "start_time": 613235.0,
      "end_time": 615667.0,
      "text": "Here&#39;s the key, if you&#39;ve missed it:"
    },
    {
      "index": 200,
      "start_time": 615691.0,
      "end_time": 620672.0,
      "text": "At day 340, we see the rise in the cancer DNA in the blood."
    },
    {
      "index": 201,
      "start_time": 620696.0,
      "end_time": 624912.0,
      "text": "That means we are catching this cancer over a hundred days earlier"
    },
    {
      "index": 202,
      "start_time": 624936.0,
      "end_time": 626413.0,
      "text": "than traditional methods."
    },
    {
      "index": 203,
      "start_time": 626921.0,
      "end_time": 629734.0,
      "text": "This is a hundred days earlier where we can give therapies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 204,
      "start_time": 629758.0,
      "end_time": 633770.0,
      "text": "a hundred days earlier where we can do surgical interventions,"
    },
    {
      "index": 205,
      "start_time": 633101.0,
      "end_time": 636134.0,
      "text": "or even a hundred days less for the cancer to grow"
    },
    {
      "index": 206,
      "start_time": 636158.0,
      "end_time": 639280.0,
      "text": "or a hundred days less for resistance to occur."
    },
    {
      "index": 207,
      "start_time": 640502.0,
      "end_time": 644676.0,
      "text": "For some patients, this hundred days means the matter of life and death."
    },
    {
      "index": 208,
      "start_time": 645237.0,
      "end_time": 647560.0,
      "text": "We&#39;re really excited about this information."
    },
    {
      "index": 209,
      "start_time": 648359.0,
      "end_time": 651456.0,
      "text": "Because of this assignment, we&#39;ve done additional studies now"
    },
    {
      "index": 210,
      "start_time": 651480.0,
      "end_time": 652742.0,
      "text": "in other cancers,"
    },
    {
      "index": 211,
      "start_time": 652766.0,
      "end_time": 656101.0,
      "text": "including breast cancer, lung cancer"
    },
    {
      "index": 212,
      "start_time": 656125.0,
      "end_time": 657346.0,
      "text": "and ovarian cancer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 213,
      "start_time": 657888.0,
      "end_time": 662238.0,
      "text": "and I can&#39;t wait to see how much earlier we can find these cancers."
    },
    {
      "index": 214,
      "start_time": 664174.0,
      "end_time": 665641.0,
      "text": "Ultimately, I have a dream,"
    },
    {
      "index": 215,
      "start_time": 666214.0,
      "end_time": 668480.0,
      "text": "a dream of two vials of blood,"
    },
    {
      "index": 216,
      "start_time": 669356.0,
      "end_time": 673221.0,
      "text": "and that, in the future, as part of all of our standard physical exams,"
    },
    {
      "index": 217,
      "start_time": 673245.0,
      "end_time": 675173.0,
      "text": "we&#39;ll have two vials of blood drawn."
    },
    {
      "index": 218,
      "start_time": 675641.0,
      "end_time": 678983.0,
      "text": "And from these two vials of blood we will be able to compare"
    },
    {
      "index": 219,
      "start_time": 679700.0,
      "end_time": 682517.0,
      "text": "the DNA from all known signatures of cancer,"
    },
    {
      "index": 220,
      "start_time": 682542.0,
      "end_time": 686489.0,
      "text": "and hopefully then detect cancers months to even years earlier."
    },
    {
      "index": 221,
      "start_time": 687179.0,
      "end_time": 689350.0,
      "text": "Even with the therapies we have currently,"
    },
    {
      "index": 222,
      "start_time": 689374.0,
      "end_time": 691975.0,
      "text": "this could mean that millions of lives could be saved."
    },
    {
      "index": 223,
      "start_time": 691999.0,
      "end_time": 696170.0,
      "text": "And if you add on to that recent advancements in immunotherapy"
    },
    {
      "index": 224,
      "start_time": 696194.0,
      "end_time": 697486.0,
      "text": "and targeted therapies,"
    },
    {
      "index": 225,
      "start_time": 697510.0,
      "end_time": 699682.0,
      "text": "the end of cancer is in sight."
    },
    {
      "index": 226,
      "start_time": 700754.0,
      "end_time": 702911.0,
      "text": "The next time you hear the word \"cancer,\""
    },
    {
      "index": 227,
      "start_time": 702935.0,
      "end_time": 705361.0,
      "text": "I want you to add to the emotions: hope."
    },
    {
      "index": 228,
      "start_time": 706123.0,
      "end_time": 707281.0,
      "text": "Hold on."
    },
    {
      "index": 229,
      "start_time": 708162.0,
      "end_time": 711735.0,
      "text": "Cancer researchers all around the world are working feverishly"
    },
    {
      "index": 230,
      "start_time": 711759.0,
      "end_time": 712915.0,
      "text": "to beat this disease,"
    },
    {
      "index": 231,
      "start_time": 712939.0,
      "end_time": 714968.0,
      "text": "and tremendous progress is being made."
    },
    {
      "index": 232,
      "start_time": 715776.0,
      "end_time": 717743.0,
      "text": "This is the beginning of the end."
    },
    {
      "index": 233,
      "start_time": 718200.0,
      "end_time": 720329.0,
      "text": "We will win the war on cancer."
    },
    {
      "index": 234,
      "start_time": 720681.0,
      "end_time": 722545.0,
      "text": "And to me, this is amazing news."
    },
    {
      "index": 235,
      "start_time": 723130.0,
      "end_time": 724180.0,
      "text": "Thank you."
    },
    {
      "index": 236,
      "start_time": 724204.0,
      "end_time": 728724.0,
      "text": "(Applause)"
    }
  ]
}